snippet.title: Ask Dr. Husky | Two Point Hospital Console
snippet.description: Dr. Husky (Lead Designer, Ben Huskins) is here to answer your questions about Two Point Hospital on console. Last week, we got the Two Point Hospital community to ask Dr. Husky some questions about the console version, and anything else that came to mind - they certainly didn't disappoint!
